{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">2D Physics Mayhem!</h2><br>Robozarro is a physics-based, 2-D action game, where robots B0-3 and 0-Ramatron embark on an epic quest through the outskirts, underbelly, and rooftops of Mech Angeles, to uncover the mystery surrounding the disappearance of Dr. Zarro.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>2D physics mayhem! Robozarro uses a 2D physics engine that brings the game's action to life, creating unpredictable encounters with enemies!</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Master the &quot;Grab N Blast&quot;, a physics-manipulation tool that turns enemies and/or the environment into explosive weapons!</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Robots love junk! Collect Junk while adventuring through Mech Angeles and trade it in for Health, grenades, or ammo upgrades!</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Recover the Robo-Claw, Mega-Charge, and other gadgets that will aid in your journey across Mech Angeles!</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Gotta go fast! Unlock Time Trials Mode and attempt to beat levels with no checkpoints and/or no damage!</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"We Got Chunky","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/984300/5acffe9020dc18d7757f74bbb65c9ae6442f656c.jpg"},{"name":"Who Saw That Coming?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/984300/6c4404e8624800ade2f683bb0b5c4de4a1c860d3.jpg"},{"name":"Herbicide","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/984300/a3316a2c34e5e3cca442a9c588777dd41a04fa52.jpg"},{"name":"Too Much TV","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/984300/7164122815aeacd40e15b084e1da09dc3524458f.jpg"},{"name":"Noisy Neighbors","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/984300/8bc87ac96dd7ba32e4124003beb58bdefae85c28.jpg"},{"name":"Operation Atlantic","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steam